      <div class="story-grid">

        <div class="story-content">
          <h2>The Birth of LUMA</h2>
          <p>
            The Emirates have always held a deep fascination for me. During my travels to Al Ain,
            between lush oases and fragrant souks, I immersed myself in the beauty traditions that my grandmother
            herself knew so well.
          </p>
          <p>
            I remember her skilled hands preparing balms where the sweetness of dates blended with the strength of cloves
            and the freshness of aloe vera. These memories became an undeniable truth: these ancestral rituals needed to be
            revived and adapted to the needs of modern women.
          </p>
          <p>
            Thus, LUMA was born — a brand where every treatment carries the imprint of these traditions while offering a
            luxurious and sensorial experience, faithful to the heritage it celebrates.
          </p>

          <a class="cta-inline" href="contact.html">Embrace Elegance</a>
